</div></div>
<p>The client wanted a fun logo that represented her and the business she was promoting. She went for the clean playful design with the woman leaning against a big C. This designed was created in Photoshop. This logo was created before AI. The full color images in this post where create with AI models using the original logo as an input image. The AI images aren't meant to be perfect, they would need to go thru a few more steps to become a complete and final product, but they allow for showing logo placement of concept logos before a final logo is chosen quickly before spending the time on finished concepts and design.</p>
            ]]>
